                        <interp inst="t18421212-name-635" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN M'KAY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I was sent for, and the prisoner was given into my custody—I produce the spoons.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18421212-name-636" type="witnessName">
