                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. PIGGOTT</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> These are my spoons—the value of the pro<lb></lb>perty I lost was 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 15<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
